                  <P><B>7 Nov 2007:</B> Robert Weir elected as co-chair, =
Patrick=20
                  Durusau appointed to be TC editor=20
                  <P>Robert Weir has been elected as co-chair of the =
OASIS Open=20
                  Document Format for Office Applications (OpenDocument) =
TC. The=20
                  OpenDocument TC chair position will be shared by Rob =
Weir and=20
                  Michael Brauer now.=20
                  <P>Patrick Durusau has been appointed as the =
OpenDocument TC's=20
                  editor.=20
                  <P><B>23 Oct 2007:</B> Accessibility Guidelines =
document=20
                  approved, public review starts=20
                  <P>The OASIS Open Document Format for Office =
Applications=20
                  (OpenDocument) TC has recently approved for public =
review the=20
                  following guidelines document:=20
                  <P><A=20
                  =
href=3D"http://docs.oasis-open.org/office/office-accessibility/v1.0/cd01/=
ODF_Accessibility_Guidelines-v1.0.odt">Open=20
                  Document Format v1.1 Accessibility Guidelines Version =
1.0</A>=20
                  <P>The public review starts today, 22 October 2007, =
and ends=20
                  21 December 2007. See <A=20
                  =
href=3D"http://lists.oasis-open.org/archives/office/200710/msg00043.html"=
>announcement</A>=20
                  for details.=20
                  <HR>
<!-- End Announcements --><!-- Start Overview --><!-- Brief description =
(50-100 words) of the TC's mission and goals. Tone should=20
             be introductory in nature, suitable for an editor or novice =
