ce-accessibility">Accessibility=20
                  Subcommittee</A> and have been approved by the =
OpenDocument=20
                  TC. They are available in <A=20
                  title=3D"Visit OpenDocument v1.1 accessibility =
guidelines in OpenDocument format"=20
                  =
href=3D"http://docs.oasis-open.org/office/office-accessibility/v1.0/cd01/=
